## 🎯 CRITICAL: Multi-Tenant Security

### Row Level Security (RLS) - ALWAYS ENFORCE
```sql
-- Every table must have clinic isolation
WHERE clinic_id IN (
  SELECT clinic_id FROM clinic_members 
  WHERE user_id = auth.uid()
)
```

### Data Access Pattern - ALWAYS FILTER
```typescript
// Every query must filter by clinic_id
const { data } = useQuery({
  queryKey: ['resource', clinic_id],
  queryFn: () => getResource(clinic_id),
  select: (data) => data.filter(item => item.clinic_id === clinic_id)
})
```

### Input Validation - ALWAYS VALIDATE
```typescript
// Every form/API call must validate clinic_id
const schema = z.object({
  clinic_id: z.string().uuid(),
  // other fields...
}).refine(data => data.clinic_id, "Clinic ID required");
```

